            A <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Roman</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">street</ENAMEX> that retains a picturesque name
is Via delle <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Botteghe Oscure</ENAMEX> `<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Street of Dark Shops</ENAMEX>.'
The widening of this <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">street</ENAMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the 1930s</TIMEX> resulted not
only in the brightening (or disappearance) of the
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">shops</ENAMEX>, but also in the uncovering of important archaeological
