<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Rome</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">airport</ENAMEX>, is a bizarre structure officially called
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Palazzo della Civilt√° del Lavoro</ENAMEX>.  Its principal design
feature is the rounded openings that cover all <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</NUMEX> of
