<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Rome</ENAMEX> soberly claims that this building has been
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">nicknamed Il Colosseo Quadrato</ENAMEX> , `<ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">The Square Colosseum</ENAMEX>.'
