<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Palazzo di Groviera</ENAMEX> `The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Swiss Cheese Palace</ENAMEX>.'

            A scattering of names referring to more recent
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Roman</ENAMEX> history can be found.  At the base of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Aventine</ENAMEX>,
