note that all examples come from establishments in
and around the more <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">‚Äúelegant‚Äù resorts</ENAMEX> of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Vermont</ENAMEX>
and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">New Hampshire</ENAMEX>, although I have witnessed the
