than <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Meredith Station</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Restaurant</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Grill</ENAMEX> and
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Niteclub</ENAMEX> and certainly more than <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Meredith Bar</ENAMEX> and
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Grill</ENAMEX> .  The <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">series</ENAMEX> in this example helps to establish a
set of alternative uses of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Meredith Station</ENAMEX> and the
