<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">appositive</ENAMEX> and the low key or off-beat opening.  Colanders
The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Vermont Housewares Outlet</ENAMEX> uses the definite
<ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">article</ENAMEX> in the apposition to suggest both uniqueness
