name, namely, grig ; and in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Wales</ENAMEX> it is called
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">grug</ENAMEX> (pronounced <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">‚ÄúGREEG‚Äù</ENAMEX>); both words are <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Celtic</ENAMEX>,
